WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
The Patens editor. Lowercase a selected, empty canvas.

00:03.000 --> 00:08.400
One pen stroke draws the a — bowl, stem, exit tail.

00:08.400 --> 00:11.000
Trace: the sketch becomes Bézier contours.

00:11.000 --> 00:15.800
The audit reads the new glyph. One click applies a fix.

00:15.800 --> 00:20.600
The Spacing tab. The pair V-a loads in the kerning editor.

00:20.600 --> 00:25.100
Nudge buttons tighten the pair; kern(V, a) updates live.

00:25.100 --> 00:30.200
Export OTF — a real OpenType file lands on disk.

00:30.200 --> 00:31.700
Back in the editor. The a is finished.
